<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Minuteman Auditorium</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container header">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" class="logo">
    </div>
    <div class="container movie-details">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 left-box">
                <h1>INCEPTION</h1>
                <p>A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O., but his tragic past may doom the project and his team to disaster.</p>
                <p>Cast:</p>
                <div class="casting">
                    <img src="/images/cast1.jpg" title="Leonardo DiCaprio">
                    <img src="/images/cast2.jpg" title="Callian Murphy">
                    <img src="/images/cast3.jpg" title="Joseph Gordon-Levitt">
                    <img src="/images/cast4.jpg" title="Elliot Page">
                    <img src="/images/cast5.jpg" title="Marion Cotillard">
                </div>
                <a href="/check">Watch Now</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                <img src="/images/inception.jpg" class="movie-img">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container series">
        <h3>Other Christopher Nolan Movies</h3>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <img src="/images/interstellar.jpg">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <img src="/images/tenet.jpg">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <img src="/images/darkknight.jpg">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <img src="/images/insomnia.jpg">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>